Header: Ozonesondes - Electrochemical Concentration Cell (En-Sci), iMet-1-RSB Radiosondes
PI_CONTACT_INFO: 8800 Greenbelt Rd, Bldg 33, Room E316,  Greenbelt, MD 20771, 301-614-5549; email: john.t.sullivan@nasa.gov
INSTRUMENT_INFO: ECC Ozonesonde with 0.5% KI half buffer solution with 5ATBMT pump corrections, attached to iMet-1-RSB radiosonde. See DM contact for more information
UNCERTAINTY:  ~5-10% in troposphere, ~5% in stratosphere, see Witte et al., (2018, JGR) for more details

STIPULATIONS_ON_USE:  Please consult PI prior to use/publication, and ensure the data have not been updated since your download.  Use of data should include an offer of co-authorship on any manuscript to PI and DM.
R0: Ozonesonde data have been reprocessed according to WMO standards following the ASOPOS Panel (Smit et al., 2012) and Witte et al. (2017, JGR)
